%N A039104 Numbers whose base-9 representation has the same number of 4's and 7's.
%H A039104 Chris R. Rehmann, <a href="/A039104/b039104.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000</a>
%t A039104 Select[Range[0, 110], DigitCount[#, 9, 4]==DigitCount[#, 9, 7]&] (* _Chris R. Rehmann_, Mar 23 2026 *)
%o A039104 (MATLAB) x = 0:21579; d = dec2base(x,9)-'0'; a = x(sum(d==4,2)==sum(d==7,2)); disp(regexprep(num2str(a), ' +', ', ')) % _Chris R. Rehmann_, Mar 23 2026
